What's new?

===========

Well to start off have I increased the look of it.

- Improved spawn (again)
- Added more details and decals
- Changed texture in level 2
- Changed some lightning to
- Changed so some puzzles doesn't kill, they only teleport you back.


-------------------------------------------


This is probaply my last release. Of course if somethings wrong do I reupload in another version name so it's really important that you report bugs and things that not how it's supposed to be!
Please, give me feedback on my new map and rate and comment. Subscribe to if you like the map? :) I hope you do enjoy this map, this is a fixed version of my first map that I did.

Steam ID: http://steamcommunity.com/id/ibeasty/
